hw3: Projections

Jason Lubrano
CSCI4229/5229 Fall 2018

Draw a mech army
demonstrate orthogonal & prespective projections
demonstrate various scaling, rotation, and translations for multiple mechs

Key bindings
	m/M 		Toggle between perspective and orthogonal
	+/- 		Changes field of view for perspective
	a/A 		Toggle axes
	arrows 		Change view angle
	PgDn/PgUp 	Zoom in and out
	0 			Reset view angle
	ESC 		Exit
